<HEAD>Vice President to Visit South Korea, Japan, Philippines</HEAD>
<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Vice President Dan Quayle will travel next
month to South Korea, Japan and the Philippines, his office
announced today.
   Quayle's Sept. 19-28 trip will include meetings with South
Korean President Roh Tae-woo and other officials.
