   Stock prices were mixed in active trading early
today.
   The Dow Jones average of 30 industrials, which surged more than
41 points Monday to move closer to its record high, was up 0.38 by
11 a.m. EDT to 2,694.61.
   Among broader market indicators, the New York Stock Exchange
